      "content": "hey, im 5 months pregnant and i have such a bad sinus infection... my head is pounding and i cant breathe through my nose at all. i have some ciprofloxacin left over from a previous infection, is it okay if i take that to clear this up? also can i take some Sudafed for the congestion?",
