      "content": "wait, r u saying i shouldn't take the cipro? i'm 5 months along so i'm way past the first trimester... i thought that was the only time things were really risky. i really need to get this infection under control before it gets worse. is the sudafed really okay though? i read somewhere that decongestants might affect blood flow to the placenta",
