      "content": "okay thanks. i'm just really tired of feeling so sick. if i take the cipro, how much should i take? like just a single dose to see if it works or should i finish the whole bottle i have left? and for the sudafed, i have the 60mg tablets, can i just take two of them at once if the congestion is really bad?",
